function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)
	
	tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i = 1, #tPlayers do
		if Hydra.ActorsInSameLevelArea(idActor, tPlayers[i]) then
			Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_LILITH, tPlayers[i])
		end
	end
	-- Amalgam run away logic
	Hydra.QActorEnableAI(ID_AMALGAM_OF_RAGE, false);
	
	Hydra.QActorPower(ID_AMALGAM_OF_RAGE, FLEEING_HOWL_POWER);
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_AMALGAM_OF_RAGE, Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_AMALGAM_OF_RAGE, "FleeSpot")[1], "AmalgamOfRage_Run", false);
	
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(ID_AMALGAM_OF_RAGE, Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_AMALGAM_OF_RAGE, "LookAt")[1])

	Hydra.Wait(0.1)

	Hydra.QActorEnableAI(ID_AMALGAM_OF_RAGE, false)
	
	Hydra.QActorPower(ID_AMALGAM_OF_RAGE, FLEEING_LEAP_POWER) 

	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_AMALGAM_OF_RAGE, 2.0)
end
